More exciting news and exciting panel information! Join us Sunday April 2 at #ETSUCON2023 to meet Olabodé Alaka for his discussion “How I Went from Gamer to Concept Artist” 👾

Bodé is a ETSU Alumni working at Epic Games currently as a concept artist for worldwide phenomenon Fortnite. Join us on Sunday to hear from an industry professional, and learn about his experience coming from our small college in the mountains! ✨

Hosted by @etsuedge

Some highlights from kimodameshi 2023 last month.
It’s a challenge where you draw figures everyday and post it in the discord sever for a month but if you miss a day you get kicked out of the server ! Pretty fun to challenge myself to practice everyday for full month. Felt like I really learned a few new things about anatomy. Ngl there were some days that I got super lazy lol.
#kimodameshi2023 
#practice #digitalart

Here's the Final concept art for the OG Fortnite Season's Raven Team Leader! She's a fusion of the Cuddle Team Leader and Raven. Working with the original creator of both, Ben Shafer, was an amazing experience, and his smile when I shared the concept was priceless. The love this character received online has been incredible. A big shoutout to the whole team for bringing her to life!
#fortnite #fortniteog

Next up is Renegade Lynx! Had a blast designing her! I blended elements from both Renegade Raider and Lynx to create a cool fusion! She looks fantastic In-game! Shout out to the team for bringing her to life as well!
#Fortnite #fortniteog

It's Yah boi Lil Split! It was so much fun designing this fusion of Peely and Lil' Whip. I didn't expect the sound team and animation team to both make a stellar track and a dance emote to go along with him! It all came out so dope! Shout out to the team for bringing him to life! #fortnite #fortniteog

Next up is Brite Hunter! He's a combo of Brite Gunner and Rex! Had fun with the helmet design and wanted to push the gnarliness of it. Once again the Team always does an immaculate job bringing these characters to life! I still can't believe I had the opportunity to design all these characters for this OG-inspired season!
#Fortnite #fortniteog
